}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "V1_210825" and "OWL-Factory-3568" are silk-screened on the SoM. :"2022/09/06" and "OPC_H68K_V2" are silk-screened on the Carrier Board. :"2022/09/06" and "OPC_H68K_TOP_V2" are silk-screened on the Expansion Board.
===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Rockchip]] RK3568 @2.0GHz :SoC: Quad-core ARM (Cortex-A55); NPU: 0.8 TOPS *GPU: ''Mali-G52 MP2'' @650MHz (OpenGL ES3.2, OpenCL 2.0) :VPU (with 4K VP9 and 4K 10-bit H265/H264 decoding) *Storage: 32GB (eMMC) Flash, TF card (max.128GB)/MMC card *Memory: 4GB (LPDDR4X) RAM *USB: 1x USB 3.0 Type-A port, 1x USB 3.0 Type-C port, 2x USB 2.0 Type-A ports *Network: 2x 1GbE ports, 2x 2.5GbE ports *WiFi: [[MediaTek]] MT7921 ((802.11bgn/ac/ax) via M.2 E-Key *Power Source: 5-24V via barrel or 5V via USB Type-C
